Re Allegheny sample confirmation draftThank you for your response unfortunately the document attached was prepared for a power deal versus a gas deal Please let me know if you would like me to update the appropriate language or if you rather send me an updated template ie watts to mmbtu Please advise Thank you Janie From Sara Shackleton on AM To Janie CT cc Melissa Ann CT Subject Re Allegheny sample confirmation draft Janie I prepared a format last week for Allegheny for use until the ISDA Master Agreement is executed Let me know if you have any questions Sara Shackleton Enron North America Corp Smith Street EB a Houston Texas phone fax Forwarded by Sara ShackletonHOUECT on AM Sara Shackleton PM To Kimberly NRON cc Subject Re Allegheny sample confirmation draft Kim It looks fine and you should use this format until the ISDA is executed We spoke with Allegheny this morning and they promise to execute next week Sara Shackleton Enron North America Corp Smith Street EB a Houston Texas phone fax Kimberly NRON PM To Sara CT cc Subject Re Allegheny sample confirmation draft Hi Sara Attached are the changes you requested Shall I begin confirming all Allegheny deals on this form until the ISDA is complete Thanks for your help Kimberly Hundl x From Sara CT on PM To Kimberly NRON cc Subject Re Allegheny sample confirmation draft Kim Attached are my comments Sara Shackleton Enron North America Corp Smith Street EB a Houston Texas phone fax Kimberly NRON AM To Sara CT cc Melissa Ann CT Subject Allegheny sample confirmation draft Hi Sara Ok I think I have properly referenced the side letter in this confirmation Please let me know what changes should be made PS I am leaving at noon today so if I havent heard from you by then I will give you a call tomorrow morning Thanks Kim x
